what to do with it. I would get it, and then in less than a week, it was just . . . GONE! Those days were challenging, embarrassing and frustrating.
 
This is why I wanted to spend a whole episode talking about 10 things to NOT do when we get our paycheck. (Believe me, I’ve done some STUPID stuff with my paycheck, and I wish someone had told me this sooner.) Go check out the full episode to learn how to avoid those money mistakes so you can start stacking some serious cash.
 
Click the link in my bio.

node.title: TRANSPARENT || I remember getting my paycheck on a Friday and not knowing

are individuals who have a good sense of their financial future. They aren’t tempted by day-to-day wants or culture.

Make sure to check out the full show. Link is in my bio.
